{"tid":2209271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瘋狂徵糧！支那下達不可能糧食儲備指標 山西貧困縣僅達標一半","createTime":"2020-09-19T13:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T15:04:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"295d7937b33c008384ce03471d81938af71e18c3","tid":2209271,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/9/18/n12414545.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F9%2F18%2Fn12414545.htm&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=ff4021ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/9/18/n12414545.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b535b3363a9981868018fc49b968246147c95566","tid":2209271,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"【大紀元2020年09月19日訊】（大紀元記者李淨報導）山西省當局曾要求壺關縣建立縣級儲備糧1,000萬斤，但這個國家級貧困縣的儲糧規模目前距離上級指標還相差一半，難以保障縣域內糧食安全。此前中共曾下令各地「糧食產量只增不減」，被輿論質疑中國或陷入糧食危機。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞報導，山西省長治市壺關縣政府網站消息，壺關縣糧食中心近日發布《關於國有糧庫和監管情況的調研》稱，2014年市政府與壺關縣政府簽訂了《糧食安全目標責任書》，明確要求壺關縣需建立縣級儲備糧1,000萬斤。<br />\n<br />\n而該縣實際只建立了500萬斤縣儲備糧，儲備品種為小麥200萬斤、玉米300萬斤，與上級政府要求的儲備規模還相差500萬斤。現有的儲糧規模難以保障縣域內糧食安全。<br />\n<br />\n根據公開資料顯示，壺關縣隸屬於山西省長治市，轄區內有6個鎮、6個鄉、1個開發區，總人口近30萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2e6042d69df8175970bd9a302e9fad90fbed58","tid":2209271,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"糧都徵唔到<br />\n打仗俾人秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fac1eccc1629467c336dcae212f6e7cb22305a8","tid":2209271,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"遲早咁搞法<br />\n搞出一個大饑荒出嚟"},{"pid":"7c00e41e529236510ac52bbc9601583e6a471c7e","tid":2209271,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:11:47.000Z","msg":"D數可以篤出黎,鐘意篤幾大又得<br />\n驚閪"},{"pid":"f1ae4c2bf8791095c56d0f0487d088923b3a5f0b","tid":2209271,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fac1eccc1629467c336dcae212f6e7cb22305a8","tid":2209271,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"遲早咁搞法<br />\n搞出一個大饑荒出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"唔係遲早<br />\n上半年已經成堆神棍磚家講緊2020下半年飢荒"},{"pid":"fdb22dd805ae239694c277ecb929d1cf3c217070","tid":2209271,"uid":340088,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"大紀元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3f01486af8a60b55553a14723f6c5b9283a2d8","tid":2209271,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79fb46bf95ad2b5ac14b98f67a620291a259706","tid":2209271,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c00e41e529236510ac52bbc9601583e6a471c7e","tid":2209271,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:11:47.000Z","msg":"D數可以篤出黎,鐘意篤幾大又得<br />\n驚閪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"有事就糧倉失火<br />\n無事就蓋蓋糧倉做做樣"},{"pid":"06c1c52f999f9732b924d4a83d648ccc7ae0f8ed","tid":2209271,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"自己都買咗兩包米放屋企"},{"pid":"92cf5471ac0428200a8f4b3af52bc1def01a1c37","tid":2209271,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc